data.description: Welcome to your new home that's been masterfully updated with modern touch's, beautiful floorpan, and a POOL in your backyard oasis to escape the Texas heat! This house has everything including a new roof and gutters, a beautiful kitchen, and a recently remodeled main bathroom. It will be easy to entertain in this home because of the open concept with the living, dining and kitchen being connected. Located in the exemplary Burleson ISD, this home's location has easy access to the highway, many great restaurants, and just minutes from Old Town Burleson and Babes Chicken! You do not want to miss out on this home for your family. The home has everything, now all it needs is YOU!
